You would have no Environmental Protection Agency?"

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:12.440
"Definitely have no EPA, absolutely."

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:13.840
“Let’s abolish the IRS.”

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:17.720
