00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:34.280
“I’m going to cut – big, big – Department of Education.”

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:37.520
"Yeah, me cut education big big!"

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:40.440
While Trump has yet to actually abolish any departments,

00:09:40.440 --> 00:09:44.480
he *has* appointed Betsy DeVos, an anti-public-school billionaire,

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:46.800
and Scott Pruitt, a climate-change denier

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:49.860
who constantly sued the EPA as attorney general, to head them,

00:09:49.860 --> 00:09:53.440
which is essentially putting a time bomb in both departments.

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:58.120
And while Republicans aren’t asking us to donate to some sort of voluntary grandma fund,

00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:02.040
Republican plans for social programs include work requirements for Medicaid,

00:10:02.040 --> 00:10:05.440
cutting Social Security and privatizing Medicare.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:07.720
Which is like meeting libertarians in the middle.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:09.760
Of the libertarian platform.

00:10:09.800 --> 00:10:11.280
Side note:

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:13.880
Why does their logo look like a sewer lid?

00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:18.320
These libertarian free-market ideals are even catching on in liberal Silicon Valley.

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:22.600
And that’s because many of the billionaires at the top of the food chain are self-described libertarians,

00:10:22.600 --> 00:10:26.640
like Thiel, or Elon Musk and former Uber CEO Travis Kalanick.

00:10:26.640 --> 00:10:30.300
Libertarians have formed a symbiotic relationship with liberal tech companies because

00:10:30.300 --> 00:10:35.640
they offer capitalist solutions to problems that are largely caused by capitalism.

00:10:35.640 --> 00:10:37.680
“The model of the future is Uber.

00:10:37.680 --> 00:10:44.880
It’s Uber everything, it's Uber accountant, it's Uber doctor, it's Uber electrician, it's Uber plumber."

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:50.240
Uh, does anyone else think that sounds suspiciously similar to the Galbladders R Us plan?

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:52.600
I'm pretty sure Gary Johnson just has one plan.

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:57.520
The libertarian ideology has been pulling mainstream politics to the right for decades now.

00:10:57.520 --> 00:11:03.560
This belief that the free market is god is now so deeply embedded in our politics that liberals –

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:08.000
who define themselves as being against racism, sexism and classism –

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:13.440
now completely ignore the role of capitalism in creating racism, sexism and classism.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:18.520
When you ignore the effects of someone’s economic beliefs that lead to discriminatory practices

00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:21.440
because that person says they’re socially liberal,

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:23.880
you end up looking at people like Rand Paul and going,

00:11:23.880 --> 00:11:25.800
"Eh, he's basically Malcom X.

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:28.160
I mean he's fiscally conservative,

00:11:28.160 --> 00:11:29.720
but socially Malcom X."

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:33.920
And while libertarian ideology made the Democratic Party more corporatist,

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:37.480
it’s made the Republican Party into Ayn Rand’s wet dream.

00:11:37.480 --> 00:11:41.600
Look, I’m not saying that the Republican Party has gone full libertarian, OK?

00:11:41.600 --> 00:11:46.200
So before someone from Reason Magazine sees this and has an "Um Actually" stroke,

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:48.800
please just relax, take a breath,

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:51.000
rub your copy of “Atlas Shrugged”

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:55.040
and squeeze your Milton Friedman Dakimakura body pillow.

00:11:55.040 --> 00:11:59.800
America will never go full libertarian because going full libertarian

00:11:59.800 --> 00:12:02.560
isn’t really what libertarian billionaires are shooting for.

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:06.080
Libertarian candidates talk a big game about individual freedoms like

00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:10.680
gay marriage and legalized drugs, but the libertarian donor class is happy

00:12:10.680 --> 00:12:15.520
to throw the social part of their platform under the bus to get their economic goals fulfilled.

00:12:15.520 --> 00:12:20.640
Listen, I don’t hate libertarians. Some of my best parents are libertarians.

00:12:20.640 --> 00:12:24.920
And I actually kind of respect their idealism and the stringency of their beliefs,

00:12:24.920 --> 00:12:29.280
you know,  the same way I respect the idealism and stringency of the Branch Davidians

00:12:29.280 --> 00:12:30.480
or ISIS.

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:32.640
But just like any fringe radical group,

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:36.800
we probably should not let them so close to the reins of power.

